<L>__{interior subway platform continuous}
<A>__{walter walks along the subway platform. he stops about midway and sits down on a bench. the uptown subway train enters and obscures our view of him. finally the train pulls away. walter is still sitting but now he is playing his drum. he is fully committed. another train wipes frame.}
